plan a class arts outing arts at stanford university presented by sica home search this site arts enews subscribe for faculty staff plan a class arts outing class outings to arts events and destinations can enrich the curriculum and deepen students understanding of and engagement with course material sica farm aid grants provide support to encourage faculty to include arts events and trips in their courses click here to learn more and apply to farm aid a note on transportation sica farm aid grants generally only support ticket costs bus rental can cost almost $1000 per bus which seats only 55 students we encourage you to look into alternative modes of transportation carpooling public transit or van rental a note on student commitment we have found that charging students a small portion of the ticket cost will guarantee that they are more committed to attending the event consider collecting student fees early on to guarantee their commitment additional funding we encourage you to discuss with your department about additional sources to supplement farm aid funds students at the san francisco symphony connect announcements sica presents visiting artists mailing list resources find funding bring an artist plan a class arts outing publicize events courses find a student to back to arts at stanford make a gift volunteer login press sitemap contact connect twitter facebook vimeo flickr 2011 stanford university all rights reserved local user login
